##This package has been deprecated. 

This package has been deprecated in favor of the [dokany](https://chocolatey.org/packages/dokany) package. 

This redistributable package is the same as the [dokany](https://chocolatey.org/packages/dokany) package with the addition of [KB2999226](https://chocolatey.org/packages/KB2999226) and [vcredist2017](https://chocolatey.org/packages/vcredist2017) bundled in. These dependencies are already part of the [dokany](https://chocolatey.org/packages/dokany) package, making this one redundant. [REFERENCE](https://github.com/cryptomator/cryptomator-win/issues/11) 

**[PACKAGE NOTES](https://github.com/bcurran3/ChocolateyPackages/blob/master/dokany-redistributable/readme.md)**
